<section class="card">
  <h2>Understanding Probability Levels</h2>

  <p>
    Frost dates are often reported at:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>50% probability:</strong> Frost occurs half the time after this date</li>
    <li><strong>30% probability:</strong> Lower risk threshold</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    A ‚Äúlast frost date‚Äù does not mean frost cannot occur afterward ‚Äî
    only that it becomes less likely.
